videoDetails.Title: Ground RB Tips to Improve at Low tiers
videoDetails.Description:
In this War Thunder video I go over some tips I have learned that helps me at lower tiers within War thunder. We Go over how to use SPAA and 4 other playstyles players should know at low tiers before they get to top tier.

Timestamps
0:00 Intro
1:04 SPAA How to aim
3:00 SPAA tips
4:41 Gun and track META
6:10 Why you should Wiggle
7:00 Range Find Targets using the Capture points
8:20 Outro More Tips
